---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---
<ServiceLayout
  title="About HullSafe"
  description="Professional robotic hull cleaning & inspection across South Devon. Powered by Keelcrab Pro technology from Italy. Learn about our mission, technology, and service area."
  heroTitle="About HullSafe"
  heroSubtitle="Professional robotic hull cleaning & inspection — bringing world-class Italian marine technology to South Devon."
  heroImage="/images/keelcrab/keelcrab-pontoon-setup.jpg"
  heroBadge="Powered by Keelcrab"
  ctaText="Get in Touch"
>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission-grid">
        <div class="mission-content">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="lead">To make professional hull maintenance accessible, affordable, and eco-friendly for every boat owner in South Devon.</p>
          <p>Traditional hull cleaning methods — dive teams, pressure washing, lift-outs — are expensive, disruptive, and often harmful to both your antifouling paint and the marine environment. We believe there's a better way.</p>
          <p>HullSafe uses advanced robotic technology to clean and inspect hulls in the water, without divers, without lift-outs, and without compromising your antifouling coating. Every clean is camera-documented, eco-compliant, and delivered at a fraction of the traditional cost. Photos and video are sent directly to your smartphone — so you can see the condition of your hull even if you're not on site.</p>
          <p>We serve boat owners across Brixham, Torquay, and Dartmouth — from 25ft sailing yachts to 60ft motor cruisers — with a simple, transparent, per-metre pricing model.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-values">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon">🎯</div>
            <h3>Precision</h3>
            <p>A.N.C.C.P certified nylon brushes proven not to remove hard matrix antifouling — extending its useful life.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon">🌊</div>
            <h3>Eco-Responsibility</h3>
            <p>All debris captured in the Keelcrab Bag. Nothing enters the water. Marina approved.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon">📹</div>
            <h3>Transparency</h3>
            <p>HD video documentation of every clean and inspection. See exactly what we see.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon">💰</div>
            <h3>Fair Pricing</h3>
            <p>Simple per-metre pricing. No hidden fees. Subscription plans for regular savings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technology -->
  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header">
        <span class="badge badge--accent">The Technology</span>
        <h2>Powered by Keelcrab Pro</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Italian-engineered robotic hull cleaning technology, developed with EU Horizon 2020 research funding.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-grid">
        <div class="tech-specs">
          <h3>Keelcrab Pro — Key Specifications</h3>
          <dl class="spec-list">
            <dt>Cleaning Speed</dt><dd>Up to 7 m² per minute</dd>
            <dt>Brush System</dt><dd>3 interchangeable types — nylon (standard), soft (delicate coatings), hard (heavy fouling)</dd>
            <dt>Camera</dt><dd>HD WiFi camera with live video feed</dd>
            <dt>Cable</dt><dd>20m Kevlar-reinforced tether</dd>
            <dt>Debris Capture</dt><dd>Keelcrab Bag — eco-compliant filtration system</dd>
            <dt>Certification</dt><dd>A.N.C.C.P. certified — safe for antifouling paints</dd>
            <dt>Max Vessel</dt><dd>Up to ~20m (larger by arrangement)</dd>
            <dt>Transport</dt><dd>Complete carry case system — fully portable</dd>
          </dl>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-video">
          <div class="video-embed">
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4DRgeDxJmjI" title="Keelcrab — Best Hull Cleaning Maintenance" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Keelcrab Story -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header">
        <h2>The Keelcrab Story</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="story-content">
        <p>Keelcrab is a registered trademark of <strong>Aeffe S.R.L.</strong>, an all-Italian innovative SME that developed this technology to reduce boat maintenance costs while maximising performance and efficiency. Their philosophy is a constant pursuit of the balance between technology and eco-sustainability.</p>
        <p>With backing from the <strong>EU Horizon 2020</strong> research programme, Keelcrab has developed a range of underwater cleaning robots where <strong>the biocide is replaced by robotic cleaning</strong> — reducing reliance on toxic antifouling chemicals through regular mechanical maintenance carried out in total safety on site.</p>
        <p>Today, boat owners from all over the world request Keelcrab service through <strong>300+ Keelcrab Points across 30 countries</strong>. HullSafe is proud to be South Devon's authorised Keelcrab Point, bringing this world-class Italian technology to local marinas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-stats">
        <div class="trust-stat">
          <span class="trust-stat__value">300+</span>
          <span class="trust-stat__label">Keelcrab Points worldwide</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-stat">
          <span class="trust-stat__value">30</span>
          <span class="trust-stat__label">Countries</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-stat">
          <span class="trust-stat__value">20%</span>
          <span class="trust-stat__label">Fuel savings from a clean hull</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-stat">
          <span class="trust-stat__value">EU</span>
          <span class="trust-stat__label">Horizon 2020 funded</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Area -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header">
        <h2>Our Service Area</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Based in Brixham, covering three world-class marinas across South Devon.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <a href="/locations/brixham" class="card service-link">
          <h3 class="card__title">Brixham</h3>
          <p class="card__text">MDL Brixham Marina — 485 berths, vessels up to 18m. England's most valuable fishing port meets 21st-century marine technology.</p>
          <span class="card__cta">Explore Brixham →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/locations/torquay" class="card service-link">
          <h3 class="card__title">Torquay</h3>
          <p class="card__text">MDL Torquay Marina — 440 berths, vessels up to 30m. The English Riviera's premier 5 Gold Anchor facility.</p>
          <span class="card__cta">Explore Torquay →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/locations/dartmouth" class="card service-link">
          <h3 class="card__title">Dartmouth</h3>
          <p class="card__text">Darthaven Marina — 270 berths, vessels up to 21.3m. River Dart estuary specialist for unique fouling challenges.</p>
          <span class="card__cta">Explore Dartmouth →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</ServiceLayout>

<style>
  .mission-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-3xl); align-items: start; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .mission-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .mission-content .lead { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); }
  .mission-content p { color: var(--text-light); }

  .mission-values { display: grid; gap: var(--space-lg); }
  .value-card { background: var(--surface); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: var(--space-lg); display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); align-items: flex-start; }
  .value-card__icon { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .value-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); }
  .value-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-light); margin: 0; }

  .tech-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-3xl); align-items: start; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .tech-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .tech-specs h3 { color: var(--white); font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); }
  .spec-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr; gap: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg); }
  .spec-list dt { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
  .spec-list dd { font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin: 0; }

  .story-content { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl); text-align: center; }
  .story-content p { color: var(--text-light); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; }

  .trust-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: var(--space-xl); text-align: center; padding: var(--space-2xl); background: var(--surface); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); }
  .trust-stat__value { display: block; font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); }
  .trust-stat__label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-light); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .trust-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }

  .service-link { text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); }
  .card__cta { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: var(--space-md); display: inline-block; }
</style>
